  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether mesh fixation in laparoscopic umbilical
      hernia repair with fibrin glue is superior to tacks in terms of postoperative pain and
      recovery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
